quicssh (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Added systemd service with security hardening
  * Includes automatic certificate management
  * Optimized for bulk data transfers (SCP, SFTP)
  * Updated dependencies with latest security patches
  * Added configurable idle timeout for flaky connections
  * TLS certificate verification support and runtime reloading
  * NAT punching support
  * Custom SSH daemon address configuration

 -- Benoît Sigoure <tsuna@lrde.epita.fr>  Sun, 01 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000
